  <h2 id="integration-purpose" style="color: #27200e; margin: 30px 0 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #141414; padding-left: 15px;">YouTube Integration Purpose</h2>
  <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Our platform serves business, ministry, and educational communities by enabling content creators to:</p>
  <ol style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 30px;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Import Their Own Video Content:</strong> Users connect their YouTube channels to access their uploaded videos</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Generate Educational Materials:</strong> Transform video transcripts into study guides, discussion questions, blog posts, and quizzes</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Organize Content Libraries:</strong> Manage and categorize video content for business, ministry, and educational use</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Create Accessible Resources:</strong> Convert video content into multiple formats for broader accessibility</li>
  </ol>

