    <p style="margin-bottom: 0; line-height: 1.6;"><strong>Important:</strong> AmplifyContent.ai requests only ONE YouTube API scope for secure, read-and-write access to your YouTube channel data.</p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #141414; margin: 25px 0;">
    <h4 style="color: #27200e; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;"><code style="background-color: #f1f1f1; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; font-family: Monaco, monospace; font-size: 0.9em; color: #27200e;">https://www.googleapis.com/auth/youtube.force-ssl</code></h4>

