    <ul style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding-left: 20px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Secure read and write access to your YouTube account data over encrypted SSL/HTTPS connections</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Retrieve channel information, video metadata, playlists, and video lists</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Update video descriptions with AI-generated summaries and chapter timestamps</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6;"><strong>Data Accessed:</strong></p>
    <ul style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding-left: 20px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Channel details (name, description, subscriber count, video count)</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Video metadata (titles, descriptions, thumbnails, upload dates, durations)</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Playlist information and organization</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6;"><strong>Data Modified:</strong></p>
    <ul style="margin-bottom: 15px; padding-left: 20px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Video descriptions (AI-generated summaries and chapter timestamps appended to existing descriptions)</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Only videos you explicitly import and process are modified</li>
