    <ul style="margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Forces all YouTube API communications to use SSL/HTTPS encryption</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Protects your YouTube data during transmission between our platform and Google's servers</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 0;">Ensures industry-standard security for all YouTube API requests</li>
    </ul>
