  <h3 style="color: #27200e; margin: 25px 0 10px 0;">3. Video Description Updates (Write Access)</h3>

  <div style="background: #e8f4f8; border: 1px solid #b3d9e8; border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
    <h4 style="color: #27200e; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;">Automated Video Description Enhancement</h4>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Our platform automatically enhances your YouTube video descriptions by appending AI-generated content to help viewers discover and navigate your content more effectively.</p>
  </div>

  <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6;"><strong>What Gets Added to Video Descriptions:</strong></p>
  <ul style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 30px;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>AI-Generated Summary:</strong> A concise overview of the video's main topics and key points</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Video Chapters:</strong> Timestamped chapter markers that help viewers navigate to specific sections of your video</li>
  </ul>

  <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6;"><strong>How It Works:</strong></p>
  <ol style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 30px;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">After you import a video from your YouTube channel, our AI analyzes the video transcript</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">The AI generates a summary and chapter timestamps based on the content</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Your original video description is <strong>preserved completely</strong></li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">The AI-generated summary and chapters are <strong>appended to the end</strong> of your existing description</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">The updated description is automatically saved to your YouTube video</li>
  </ol>

  <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
    <h4 style="color: #27200e; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;">Important Safeguards:</h4>
    <ul style="margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>5000 Character Limit:</strong> YouTube enforces a maximum description length of 5000 characters. If adding our AI content would exceed this limit, we intelligently truncate the additions while preserving your original description in full.</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Original Content Protected:</strong> Your existing video description is never modified or removed</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Clear Attribution:</strong> AI-generated sections are clearly marked with headers (üìù SUMMARY and üì∫ VIDEO CHAPTERS)</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Only Your Videos:</strong> We only update descriptions for videos imported from channels you own and have authorized</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Full Control:</strong> You can manually edit or remove the AI-generated content directly on YouTube at any time</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6;"><strong>Benefits of Description Enhancement:</strong></p>
  <ul style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 30px;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Improved Discoverability:</strong> More detailed descriptions help YouTube's search algorithm understand your content</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Better User Experience:</strong> Chapter markers allow viewers to jump to specific sections</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Increased Engagement:</strong> Clear summaries help viewers decide if your video matches their needs</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Time Savings:</strong> Automatically generate content that would take hours to create manually</li>
  </ul>

