  <h3 style="color: #27200e; margin: 25px 0 10px 0;">Data Sharing Policy</h3>

  <div style="background: #e8f4f8; border: 1px solid #b3d9e8; border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
    <h4 style="color: #27200e; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;">We Do NOT Share Your YouTube Data</h4>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0; line-height: 1.6;"><strong>AmplifyContent.ai does not sell, rent, trade, or share your YouTube data with any third parties, organizations, or external entities. Your YouTube channel information, video metadata, and OAuth tokens remain exclusively within our secure platform.</strong></p>
  </div>

  <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6;"><strong>Limited Service Provider Usage:</strong></p>
  <ul style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 30px;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>AI Processing Only:</strong> Google Gemini and OpenAI receive only video transcript text for content generation. These services do NOT receive your YouTube account information, channel data, or OAuth tokens.</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>No Marketing or Analytics Sharing:</strong> We do not share YouTube data with marketing platforms, advertising networks, or analytics services.</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>No AI Training:</strong> Your YouTube data is never used to train AI models or shared with AI training datasets.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 style="color: #27200e; margin: 25px 0 10px 0;">Data Retention</h3>

  <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6;"><strong>Retention Periods:</strong></p>
  <ul style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 30px;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>YouTube Channel Data:</strong> Retained while your YouTube account remains connected to AmplifyContent.ai</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Video Metadata:</strong> Retained while your account is active and connected</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>OAuth Tokens:</strong> Retained until you disconnect your YouTube account or revoke access through Google</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Generated Content:</strong> Retained while your account is active; deleted upon account closure</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 style="color: #27200e; margin: 25px 0 10px 0;">Data Deletion</h3>

  <p style="margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6;"><strong>You can delete your YouTube data at any time through the following methods:</strong></p>
  <ul style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 30px;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Disconnect YouTube Account:</strong> Remove YouTube connection from your profile settings - deletes all YouTube data within 24 hours</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Revoke OAuth Access:</strong> Revoke AmplifyContent.ai access through Google Account settings - immediately invalidates our access and triggers data deletion</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Delete Individual Videos:</strong> Remove specific videos from your dashboard - deletes that video's metadata and generated content</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Close Account:</strong> Delete your entire AmplifyContent.ai account - permanently removes all YouTube data within 30 days</li>
  </ul>

  <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
    <h4 style="color: #27200e; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;">Automatic Deletion:</h4>
    <ul style="margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">If your account is inactive for 2 years, all data including YouTube data is automatically deleted after 90-day notice</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">When YouTube access is revoked, all associated YouTube data is automatically deleted within 24 hours</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 0;">When you close your account, all YouTube data is permanently deleted within 30 days</li>
